        <item>
            <title>1.8.0</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 22:12:38 -0600</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>29</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.8.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Version 1.8.0 — Prompt Suggestions & Smarter Cloud Generation</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>New:</strong> AI-generated story prompt suggestions appear on the creation screen with a typewriter animation — tap one to start generating instantly</li>
  <li><strong>New:</strong> Recommended models highlighted at the top of the HuggingFace text model picker</li>
  <li><strong>New:</strong> Copy Error button on error banners for easier troubleshooting</li>
  <li><strong>Improved:</strong> Cloud text generation no longer depends on on-device models — smoother experience with HuggingFace and other cloud providers</li>
  <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Creation mode tooltips now appear directly above the hovered button</li>
</ul>]]></description>
